sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant AI as AI Platform
    participant CMD as ArcKit Command
    participant TPL as Template System
    participant FS as File System
    
    U->>AI: /arckit.principles "Create cloud-first principles"
    AI->>CMD: Parse command + arguments
    CMD->>FS: Check projects/ structure
    CMD->>FS: Read .arckit/VERSION
    CMD->>TPL: Load architecture-principles-template.md
    TPL-->>CMD: Template with placeholders
    CMD->>CMD: Generate Document ID<br/>via generate-document-id.sh
    CMD->>CMD: Populate template sections
    CMD->>FS: Write ARC-000-PRIN-v1.0.md
    CMD-->>AI: Summary of created artifact
    AI-->>U: "Created architecture principles<br/>at projects/000-global/ARC-000-PRIN-v1.0.md"
